description:
Add convenience methods to ticks client for common human actions:

```go
// Approve sets verdict=approved, triggering verdict processing
func (c *Client) Approve(taskID string) error {
    return c.SetVerdict(taskID, "approved", "")
}

// Reject sets verdict=rejected with optional feedback
func (c *Client) Reject(taskID string, feedback string) error {
    return c.SetVerdict(taskID, "rejected", feedback)
}
```

These wrap the SetVerdict method but provide cleaner API for common operations.

Acceptance criteria:
- [ ] Approve method implemented
- [ ] Reject method implemented with feedback support
- [ ] Both call SetVerdict internally
- [ ] Feedback note uses --from human
